                    "company": "Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam (VU Amsterdam)",
                    "description": "I conduct research in the area of main-group (B, Al, Si, P) and organometallic chemistry with the aim of developing novel building blocks for the creation of functional materials and designed catalyst structures for (asymmetric) transition metal catalysis and (in)organocatalysis. Reactive intermediate chemistry and computational chemistry is used as an invaluable tool to analyse the processes in great depth aiming for transferable understanding.",
